<br>
Wuoshi sniffed at her, the intake of air causing the loose tendrils of hair around her face to stir. Candra shivered visibly. Its voice slipped through her mind again, searching. <!--EZCODE ITALIC START--><em><!--EZCODE BOLD START--><strong>“I smell the blood of my enemies on your flesh, and the essence of dragon-kind mingled with your own. What magic is this...?”</strong><!--EZCODE BOLD END--></em><!--EZCODE ITALIC END--><br>
